        <mxCell id="6kxt4TkcNQ4W9YgQE0m6-0" value="Define distinctions of FollowedBy against NestBy.&lt;div&gt;Follow suits Generative Schema while Nest suits Parametric Schema. Both properties can be assigned to the pattern &lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 51, 51);&quot;&gt;as one can be followed by another but not necesseraly nested by them. FollowBy is transitive and allows to trace sequance of relations, while NestBy allows to define&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="dwxlDR3IUaoGZZwB89xd-1" vertex="1">
